{"tid":1733713,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"速龍小隊配備SIG 516突擊步槍","createTime":"2019-11-18T07:17:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T04:23:06.000Z","uid":222970,"like":8,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"d2b23952582511db8db5019b113d061dd15ceaef","tid":1733713,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T07:17:09.000Z","msg":"【佐敦即時】速龍小隊配備SIG 516突擊步槍<br />\n<br />\n根據資料，SIG 516步槍每分鐘可連續發射750至950發子彈，可以配上軍用及警用5.56mm步槍槍子彈，其射程範圍遠超特勤隊過去使用的MP5衝鋒槍。以往行動中，該步槍曾負責看守高位或遠距離的隊員用作狙擊用途。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UoV3zVi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUoV3zVi.jpg&h=92dc5a8f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"897dc78a4743b705f00138d74ed45c47c986440a","tid":1733713,"uid":273716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T07:17:44.000Z","msg":"打杖？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ae1195365a9debcc4d169fb40ace0b95302f945","tid":1733713,"uid":198810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T07:18:05.000Z","msg":"推!!!!!!!有冇可能理大裏面啲人開記招?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1733677\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1733677</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ed0678675285be8913d66668ebf16f0f7d64c78e","tid":1733713,"uid":222970,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T07:21:10.000Z","msg":"香港：採用10英寸槍管型。<br />\n香港警務處<br />\n特別任務連<br />\n反恐特勤隊[13]"},{"pid":"4590a04b0500efc85b6b60b73a559eeb9d3e5e22","tid":1733713,"uid":290176,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T07:21:39.000Z","msg":"CLS <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9ec80a188725b2c0835f14e5ae17af433eaa6d0","tid":1733713,"uid":239205,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T07:28:07.000Z","msg":"屌其他國家幾時肯出兵"},{"pid":"97a6b19922090df11b8b25d30f219d6ac61a3154","tid":1733713,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed0678675285be8913d66668ebf16f0f7d64c78e","tid":1733713,"uid":222970,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T07:21:10.000Z","msg":"香港：採用10英寸槍管型。<br />\n香港警務處<br />\n特別任務連<br />\n反恐特勤隊[13]"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T07:29:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ac78f6cec67a1275f95bbf0966370a92f5eb5b9","tid":1733713,"uid":306434,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T07:30:32.000Z","msg":"分析: 唯一救埋大方法 -- 開花<br />\n<br />\n對家優勢:<br />\n武器精良<br />\n<br />\n對家缺點:<br />\n只有不足1萬防暴<br />\n唔敢入校園(圍而不攻斷吾糧草，但24小時內仲安全)<br />\n現時大部分武器，人手都集中於九龍<br />\n<br />\n結論: 人家有槍，一個可打100個，但係大型武器(eg水炮車)都集中於埋大，但其他地方(如狗聯辨，或各大狗屋，紅藍店)是最脆弱，利用快閃優勢，只要威脅到其他春袋，對家就要分兵離開埋大。威脅唔一定要勇武，1千人企係狗屋外就夠，對家冇人手驅散"},{"pid":"a48cda913fd635f60366f27d286d0ac835c897f3","tid":1733713,"uid":227588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T07:31:49.000Z","msg":"其實攞咁多大殺傷力武器出嚟，係唔係同國際宣報香港64即將上映？"},{"pid":"74332f4164ca229d06bef03dd6a3c81c425cd9a7","tid":1733713,"uid":28970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T07:31:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8bf8c5eeba9ca0effab19f6a9dd6a396fdfbf3d","tid":1733713,"uid":36421,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T07:33:57.000Z","msg":"根本佢依家當咗反恐級別去處理"},{"pid":"336f425bf62a1a218e39122928b780038b0441f1","tid":1733713,"uid":90601,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T07:35:52.000Z","msg":"其實完全無必要 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一人一枝左輪 我俾埋你AR-15一定夠頂<br />\n你搞到軍演咁 根本就係嚇鬼"},{"pid":"f826c48c7c95377c141298d6db179f4284210954","tid":1733713,"uid":176996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"